{
  "stem": "6845.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was the only girl.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we just had, like, a competition going.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Why you, and why not me?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So anyway, we got along but not as well as I got along with my other brother.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So Europe was completely changed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, and my mother was very concerned, still, about more learning.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she says, you are-- oh yeah, meantime, I proved to my mother that I can sew real well because I took some sewing-- still before I went to Brussels.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was extremely good at it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so when I came back, she says, look, you have such talent for that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Wouldn't you like to go and learn some designing in Budapest?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I say, sure, mother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I went to a very snazzy place for six weeks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "By that time, I knew Nick.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so he even came up-- What year was this?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Eight, '38. '39? '38?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Had to be '38, '39, probably '39 and-- in between.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I went to Budapest to learn this designing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I enjoyed it because really, I really had a good feeling for it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And whatever my mother thought I should learn, I want to learn.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But meantime, I started to be interested in boys-- men.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was a brand new thing because I really never paid attention to men.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had this one childhood boyfriend.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was 100% content.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was-- we were like brother, sisters, living side by side, and hoping that one day, maybe-- not-- yeah, we were really hoping we were [? mates. ?] So-- but he wasn't back in Czechoslovakia anymore.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that's the first occasion I met Nick.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I-- well, there's a fun part to that encounter because the fellow who introduced us was a friend, kind of, mine-- an attorney.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
